snippet.textDisplay: Thank you for making this about Disney. I haven’t really trusted them since the whole copyright issue. So many people I know are obsessed with Disney. I’m not denying that the movies are excellent. I’m also not denying that there is joy brought by the parks but this company has acquired almost everything that’s important to mainstream pop culture. It’s a monopoly on nostalgia.Letting one company have that much power and influence to shape our entire world is scary. I don’t think the company is pure evil but greed and power are dangerous things. Good for SONY for taking a stand. I’m guessing Disney May win in the end but at least it should be a challenge.
